<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 14:07:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列可能为参与10月7日大屠杀的哈马斯恐怖分子设立特别法庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-may-establish-special-court-for-hamas-terrorists-who-took-part-in-massacres/0000018b-94c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb00bd0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列在加沙边境附近社区关押了数百名涉嫌参与哈马斯大屠杀的人，并一直在系统地收集战争罪和反人类罪的数字证据</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 12:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-may-establish-special-court-for-hamas-terrorists-who-took-part-in-massacres/0000018b-94c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb00bd0000</guid></item><item><title>看到南部的恐怖，以色列北部的居民感到他们必须自力更生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/seeing-the-horrors-in-the-south-galilee-residents-feel-they-must-fend-for-themselves/0000018b-9469-db7e-af9b-ffebd7ad0000</link><description>私人拖拉机挖的战壕、临时搭建的射击阵地以及自愿担任观察员的平民：西加利利和上加利利的居民不再相信国家会保护他们。一位居民说，“感觉我们又回到了建州前的日子”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 11:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/seeing-the-horrors-in-the-south-galilee-residents-feel-they-must-fend-for-themselves/0000018b-9469-db7e-af9b-ffebd7ad0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部：约旦河西岸与以色列军队的冲突造成六人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-six-killed-in-west-bank-clashes-with-israeli-army/0000018b-94af-db71-a7df-fdefff020000</link><description>位于拉马拉的巴勒斯坦权力机构卫生部表示，所有六人均死于与以色列国防军冲突中的枪伤，其中两人在杰宁，两人在希伯伦附近</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 10:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-six-killed-in-west-bank-clashes-with-israeli-army/0000018b-94af-db71-a7df-fdefff020000</guid></item><item><title>又有五名以色列士兵在加沙地面行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/five-additional-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-948a-db7e-af9b-ffcbbc660000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了5名阵亡士兵的姓名，使加沙地面行动开始以来阵亡士兵总数达到24人</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 10:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/five-additional-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-948a-db7e-af9b-ffcbbc660000</guid></item><item><title>美国正在缓慢而谨慎地在加沙地带为以色列划定红线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-slowly-and-carefully-drawing-red-lines-for-israel-on-gaza/0000018b-9414-db71-a7df-fdddf39d0000</link><description>最近一周，白宫关于以色列-加沙战争的信息发生了转变，官员们谈到了加沙的人道主义暂停，总统乔·拜登向以色列施压，要求其控制极端主义的约旦河西岸定居者</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 08:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-slowly-and-carefully-drawing-red-lines-for-israel-on-gaza/0000018b-9414-db71-a7df-fdddf39d0000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉在贝鲁特发表讲话，以色列处于高度戒备状态；布林肯会见内塔尼亚胡、赫尔佐格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-live/blinken-to-push-for-humanitarian-pause-as-israeli-army-encircles-gaza-city/0000018b-9334-db7e-af9b-fbf78ad50000</link><description>24 名以色列士兵和军官在加沙地面攻势中丧生 ■ 布林肯周五降落在以色列，预计将推动以色列在加沙战斗中“人道主义暂停” ■ 官员称，美国在加沙上空飞行无人机搜寻人质 ■ 以色列国防军在黎巴嫩发动空袭导弹发射 ■ 242 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称加沙有 9,000 多人丧生</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-live/blinken-to-push-for-humanitarian-pause-as-israeli-army-encircles-gaza-city/0000018b-9334-db7e-af9b-fbf78ad50000</guid></item><item><title>在东西方之间，内塔尼亚胡现在确实处于一个联盟中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/between-east-and-west-netanyahu-really-now-is-a-league-of-his-own/0000018b-91bc-d477-a1ff-f7bc76240000</link><description>一边是乌克兰和美国，一边是卡塔尔和俄罗斯：一切都在这两个轴心之间进行。 ■ 摩萨德前任主席约西·科恩回归背后的原因是什么？ ■ 斯莫特里奇努力点燃约旦河西岸，同时永远不会忘记照顾他的基地</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/between-east-and-west-netanyahu-really-now-is-a-league-of-his-own/0000018b-91bc-d477-a1ff-f7bc76240000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉期待已久的讲话可能决定战争的进程和黎巴嫩的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-long-awaited-speech-could-dictate-the-course-of-the-war-and-lebanons-future/0000018b-9185-db71-a7df-fdcd1cda0000</link><description>美国在该地区的强大存在使真主党和伊朗更有可能保持谨慎 ■ 以色列领导人铲除哈马斯的承诺只是口头声明，他们尚未说明如何将其转化为行动 ■ 美国的合作预示着今天的美好前景以色列与哈马斯战争之后</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-long-awaited-speech-could-dictate-the-course-of-the-war-and-lebanons-future/0000018b-9185-db71-a7df-fdcd1cda0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:31:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列为民主而战。现在他正在让它为自己的生命而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</link><description>总理的助手们已经在为内塔尼亚胡战后的政治生存收集弹药，但公众不太可能让他保住自己的席位。他的继任者将不得不面对内塔尼亚胡留下的灾难性遗产</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列尚未从内塔尼亚胡时代的学说中清醒过来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-hasnt-sobered-up-yet-from-its-netanyahu-era-doctrine/0000018b-919e-d477-a1ff-f79ece710000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 00:34:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-hasnt-sobered-up-yet-from-its-netanyahu-era-doctrine/0000018b-919e-d477-a1ff-f79ece710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将税收收入转移给巴勒斯坦权力机构，但扣除流向加沙的资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-palestinian-authority-but-deducts-gaza-bound-funds/0000018b-9255-db7e-af9b-fbd7201a0000</link><description>内阁还决定，以色列将不再允许加沙工人入境，并将10月7日在以色列的加沙人送回加沙地带</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 23:47:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-palestinian-authority-but-deducts-gaza-bound-funds/0000018b-9255-db7e-af9b-fbd7201a0000</guid></item><item><title>“耶路撒冷的孩子们问我：圣诞老人，尽管有战争，你还会来吗？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-03/ty-article/.highlight/children-in-jerusalem-ask-me-santa-will-you-come-despite-the-war/0000018b-9247-db71-a7df-ffcfb7f20000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：即使在战争中，以色列唯一经过认证的圣诞老人仍为欢乐而战，度蜜月的新婚夫妇则与家乡的损失作斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 23:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-03/ty-article/.highlight/children-in-jerusalem-ask-me-santa-will-you-come-despite-the-war/0000018b-9247-db71-a7df-ffcfb7f20000</guid></item><item><title>他记录了田园诗般的基布兹的最后几年。他死于哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-captured-his-kibbutzs-final-years-he-died-in-the-hamas-massacre-that-decimated-it/0000018b-9140-db7e-af9b-fbc306ed0000</link><description>就在几个月前，Kfar Azza 的居民动员起来帮助 Yahav Winner 将基布兹变成了他的第一部故事片的拍摄地。拍摄电影和第一个孩子的出生是他一生中最幸福的日子。 10 月 7 日，他在保护家人的过程中被谋杀。他还留下了被毁社区的最后大量文件</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-captured-his-kibbutzs-final-years-he-died-in-the-hamas-massacre-that-decimated-it/0000018b-9140-db7e-af9b-fbc306ed0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对抗内塔尼亚胡的秘密武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bidens-secret-weapon-vis-a-vis-netanyahu/0000018b-91e7-db7e-af9b-fbe75acf0000</link><description>拜登总统没有责骂内塔尼亚胡，而是制定了“紧紧拥抱比比”的策略。最近的书籍揭示了两人在 2021 年加沙一轮战斗中进行的长时间会谈的内容，以及总统断言以色列停止的时候到了</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bidens-secret-weapon-vis-a-vis-netanyahu/0000018b-91e7-db7e-af9b-fbe75acf0000</guid></item><item><title>西岸好战分子斯莫特里奇必须被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/west-bank-warmonger-smotrich-must-be-fired/0000018b-919e-db71-a7df-fddfcc7e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:32:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/west-bank-warmonger-smotrich-must-be-fired/0000018b-919e-db71-a7df-fddfcc7e0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯抵达以色列推动加沙战斗“人道主义暂停”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-to-push-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-9201-db7e-af9b-fbc392870000</link><description>在前往约旦进行下一站访问之前，预计美国国务卿将向以色列总理内塔尼亚胡